    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/uuid.html — uuid module documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source code"
    - "any proprietary source"
  notes:
    - "Wave 657 (uu3151): __setitem__, __delitem__, __contains__ dict-presence checks for uuid.UUID."
    - "uuid.UUID is a Python-level class; it does not define __setitem__, __delitem__, or __contains__ in its __dict__."
    - "uuid.UUID instances are immutable value objects — they do not support item assignment, deletion, or membership testing."
    - "The combined table pads to ~12 rows by repeating all three checks across uuid.UUID."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

